    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "multi_cluster_content",
      "x": 561.0087890625,
      "y": 1504.69921875,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "Tenant-A runs ArgoCD (hub) and manages BOTH clusters.\nTenant-B is remote at 129.158.33.235:6443.\nCluster secret (SealedSecret) registers tenant-b in ArgoCD.\nServiceAccount + ClusterRoleBinding (cluster-admin) on tenant-b.",
      "originalText": "Tenant-A runs ArgoCD (hub) and manages BOTH clusters.\nTenant-B is remote at 129.158.33.235:6443.\nCluster secret (SealedSecret) registers tenant-b in ArgoCD.\nServiceAccount + ClusterRoleBinding (cluster-admin) on tenant-b.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#64748b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
